data.title: 26th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival
meta_keywords: Don't miss the 26th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival scheduled for February 16-18
data.meta_description: Don't miss the 26th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival scheduled for February 16-18, 2024 benefitting Suncoast Charities For Children.
data.text: The 26th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival is a three-day event held Feb. 16-18, 2024 at the Sarasota Fairgrounds that benefits Suncoast Charities for Children. Headline acts performing include Molly Hatchet (Friday – February 16), Grand Funk Railroad (Saturday - February 17), and Creed Fisher (Sunday – February 18). The Festival features continuous live music, over 100 vendors, freestyle motocross, charity motorcycle rides, bike shows, a motorcycle “sound off” competition, biker games, and much more! On-site camping is also available. Admission is $10 in advance and $15 at the gate (12 and under free). Limited VIP tickets are also available. For more information visit: http://thunderbythebay.org
